rows.label: qst201822_msg0001
rows.name:
So you met Gox but he
wouldn't talk to you at all?

rows.label: qst201822_msg0002
rows.name:
No, he wasn't being
even slightly helpful.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0003
rows.name: Huh, OK, so he chased you away...

rows.label: qst201822_msg0004
rows.name:
Well, it's not unheard of. Us Phonexes
are usually wary of strangers, after all.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0005
rows.name:
It's not easy to earn our trust.
Especially when it comes to humans
or Blades...

rows.label: qst201822_msg0006
rows.name:
Is that right...?
Not even poor old me...

rows.label: qst201822_msg0007
rows.name:
Oh, but don't get down in the dumps.
You should be fine if you just bring
him something to eat.

rows.label: qst201822_msg0008
rows.name: Phonexes like Pinfins a whole lot!

rows.label: qst201822_msg0009
rows.name:
If you give him that,
I'm sure his mood'll improve greatly!

rows.label: qst201822_msg0010
rows.name:
I see! So food is the key!
Why didn't I think of that?!

rows.label: qst201822_msg0012
rows.name:
OK team, let's go track down
some of that thing that Phonexes like!
